name: Synthetic Daydream
description:
Last week, my lil sister in law “Havel” showed me her latest drawing that inspired from my work, I feel so amazed coz her pieces was so awesomee, she’s 13 years old btw, and a very shy-person. 
I show her all about NFT things and ask her to collaborate, from her artwork I try to evolve and do my things like motion and 3D effect.. 
Please enjoy our first Collaboration:))
